- test_init_db_creates_schema: expects 15-column schema (lifecycle_status
  + 6 new I-arch-001a columns) instead of legacy 9-column
- test_actor_marks_completed_after_pre_insert + test_get_run_after_drain
  now mock scripts.run_honest_sweep_r3.run_one_query via monkeypatch to
  return a synthetic summary + write a minimal valid manifest. Hermetic
  acceptance — no real OpenRouter call. Asserts lifecycle_status='completed'
  + pipeline_status='success' + computed_field status alias.

P2-001: narrow OperationalError catch in get_run
- run_store.get_run now only returns None when error message contains
  'no such table'. Schema corruption / migration bugs surface instead
  of being masked as missing-row.

Smoke: 16/16 pass on tests/v6/acceptance + tests/polaris_v6/queue +
tests/polaris_graph/audit_ir.

