Addresses Codex diff iter-2 findings:

P1-003: test_dramatiq_acceptance.py scenario 1 also pre-inserts a row but
was not monkeypatched. With the new actor, row existence selects the
pipeline-A path. Applied the same _fake_run_one_query + manifest write
monkeypatch + POLARIS_V6_OUTPUT_ROOT override pattern as the sibling
test_runs_db_integration.py tests. Hermetic — no real OpenRouter call.

P2-002: legacy DB read-first-on-startup. run_store.get_run now detects
"no such column" OperationalError, runs init_db migration once, retries
the SELECT. Eliminates the 500 on a deployed legacy DB before any write.

Smoke: 17/17 pass on tests/v6/acceptance + tests/polaris_v6/queue +
tests/polaris_graph/audit_ir (24 total: 17 PASSED + 7 XFAIL).

GH#463. Codex diff iter-2 REQUEST_CHANGES addressed.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
